Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I told you, the doctor is over examining my grandma right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you there's a lot of unusual stuff here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.29,0:01:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! What a pretty inkstone!
